narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: SO GREAT. Jess is the best. Awesome mix of good readings, interesting discussions and interactive activities. Loved the creative component (projects >> papers). Light courseload (5-8 page midterm paper, final project, class presentation) and SO much fun.

Take this class! It's amazing - one of the more hands on dance classes at Yale. The required papers can be substituted with dance/film/relevanr topic projects, so you'll get a better chance to show what you're capable of. The work really isn't bad at all, and frankly it's so interesting that it's not a bother. You'll have so much fun, Jessica is amazing (take her other classes too).
